# Internal sprint planning — paybot-mcp is Apache-2.0 public; story files
# may reference operator-private workspace slugs and must not ship by default.
# Use `docs/stories/*` (not `docs/stories/`) so individual files can be
# re-included via negation patterns below. Git docs: "It is not possible to
# re-include a file if a parent directory of that file is excluded."
docs/stories/*
